ac{1}{-x}$ 的平移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":523}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"8afkgc","at":1773194003637}},"smart_blocks:试卷汇总/功底考/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05023409,-0.00501061,0.03710274,-0.05356738,0.00534686,0.00506744,0.0150794,-0.03694967,0.0419833,0.00540571,0.03067729,-0.04643659,0.0423088,-0.02045865,0.02627694,0.0311046,-0.01149291,-0.03658189,-0.08472834,-0.00978497,0.14187501,-0.03128761,-0.02357704,-0.06447012,0.041386,0.0513889,0.02704046,-0.05710584,-0.00772259,-0.18573765,0.00153613,0.01736974,-0.00818685,0.02331927,0.03494797,-0.0397455,-0.0245981,0.06903946,-0.06273811,0.03706632,-0.02186584,0.07565024,0.04945996,-0.01477129,0.03106321,-0.03806264,-0.0066231,-0.0367012,0.01395797,-0.0160351,-0.05056463,0.00655737,-0.01910599,0.02376823,0.04872048,-0.00194221,-0.01240926,0.06715662,0.00008414,-0.0144307,0.06735384,0.00567691,-0.20915787,-0.00335193,0.02749928,-0.00606903,-0.01346983,-0.06298997,0.04278512,0.07860548,-0.030893,0.02306871,0.0156106,0.06184596,0.00135509,-0.00754683,0.0144,-0.00111831,-0.08628249,-0.02120039,-0.01796584,0.08692592,0.02833899,-0.0010149,-0.01358761,-0.00127525,0.00644945,-0.07886849,-0.01345919,-0.03834623,0.00389741,-0.01085122,0.02717369,0.03815438,-0.05136524,0.02670705,0.04489834,0.02870172,-0.02156559,0.09023318,-0.03878189,0.08074678,-0.0244506,-0.09678939,0.01162603,-0.05005298,-0.04337784,-0.075477,-0.02250992,-0.01197472,-0.04287376,-0.02157421,0.063089,-0.09106115,-0.01022668,-0.00313258,0.06196336,0.04333382,-0.01633859,-0.00973987,0.04853337,0.06435674,0.03472126,-0.02231049,-0.00737104,-0.05922223,0.01734835,-0.00310653,0.07233702,0.06091616,0.04031992,0.0014637,0.04744383,0.03224611,-0.01465105